# Snapshot allow-list for install-helpers/lint-runtime-reachability.sh.
# Captured 2026-05-26 at lint introduction (TUNE-3 / 25-Q Q10).
#
# Each line below is a PRE-EXISTING dead module the lint would
# flag but is grandfathered. Cleanup tracked in TUNE-3.b
# (see worklist). This file shrinks as modules are wired up or
# deleted.
#
# Format: <file>:<module-name> per line.
# Lines starting with `#` are comments; blank lines ignored.
#
# To add a NEW entry (only with operator approval — the lint
# is the platform's dead-code defense): append the file:module
# pair AND open a worklist task referencing TUNE-3.b for its
# eventual cleanup.

